public interface QueryPartProvider
extends java.io.Serializable

This interface provides an indirection to QueryPart

All QueryPartProvider implementations are actually also QueryPart. But in order not to pollute the declared method space, the QueryPart interface is not exposed to client code

Author:
Lukas Eder
